# --- Things explicitly NOT ignored -----------------------------------
# We DO commit:
#   phase3_implementation/cache/*.npz   - small, expensive to compute, useful
#                                          for reviewers who don't want to
#                                          re-run build_ground_truth.
#   phase3_implementation/results/*.npz - the raw MC outputs that the figures
#                                          and the paper are computed from.
#   phase3_implementation/results/*.csv - the human-readable summary.
#   writeup/figures/*.pdf               - figures referenced by the writeup.
